    <body.head>
      <hedline>
        <hl1>How to Give Away $21.8 Billion</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <abstract>
        <p>Dulcianne Vye letter scores unflattering photo of Bill Gates in Jean Strouse's April 16 article on Gates Foundation</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>I can't think of anything more demoralizing than to have one's portrait in your magazine: wrinkles, age spots, scraggly chin whiskers, pleated chins all scarily exposed and larger than life. The rich and famous, powerful, gifted, sinful or righteous -- no one is safe.</p>
        <p>Dulcianne Vye  Lamoine, Me.</p>
      </block>
